TITLE: The Village 2
AUTHOR: Invictus321
E-MAIL: paradoxbass@gmail.com

FILENAME: aim_the_village2.bsp
FILESIZE: 940kb (Zip File: 271kb)
DATE RELEASED: 30 July 2006

CREDITS: I used Hammer to make this map, other than that its all my own work.

INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS: Simply put the .bsp file into USERNAME/counter strike source/cstrike/maps

DESCRIPTION**: This map is the final version of my large urban arena map. I didn't bother releasing any pre-releases because thats useless.

BUGS: If theres any bugs, I didn't find them in my hours of testing. This is a very complete version. If you find anything wrong with it tell me and i'll fix it.

COMMENTS: You'll need to let it calculate the bot NAV first time you run with bots. After that it'll be fine. Enjoy!
